{"tid":2432182,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"棍波私家車起步問題","createTime":"2021-03-04T06:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T16:15:55.000Z","uid":168897,"like":0,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"6a386454ee173411400149668ed655fced616c99","tid":2432182,"uid":168897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:29:51.000Z","msg":"本身有棍波牌但楂開自動波, 最近諗緊想換架棍私尼玩下, 但唔多熟 (本身係棍 van 牌) 暫時唔敢去試車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。想問下起步正確次序應該係: <br />\n1. 踩極力子 -&gt; 入波 -&gt; 吊極子搵 bite point  -&gt; 俾油 -&gt; 鬆手制/brake -&gt; 放曬極力子; 定係<br />\n2. 踩極力子 -&gt; 入波 -&gt; 吊極子搵 bite point   -&gt; 鬆手制/brake -&gt;  俾油  -&gt; 放曬極力子?<br />\n<br />\n如果上斜起步 (假設冇 hill assist) 又有冇唔同?  <br />\n同埋如果我剩係吊住喺 bite point 唔俾油架車會唔會死火? <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84413e65d003775283bd35539451e72294cea9f6","tid":2432182,"uid":48161,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GQIw5ltMQto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGQIw5ltMQto&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=22d71a4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GQIw5ltMQto</a>"},{"pid":"df8853f3b5a5a15dbd1ef28a187fd50988fea5ab","tid":2432182,"uid":197379,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"驚溜後咪卑左油先放手制"},{"pid":"54555af8f80b0c3b3ce942eec942b94f175aa8c8","tid":2432182,"uid":73907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"尼？"},{"pid":"7ecc832339cdce1993048cfabcc510bfdee311e9","tid":2432182,"uid":196924,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"睇嚟你個van牌都係呃返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd2b8120b56afa22a5d591425285ec5ed117a2b","tid":2432182,"uid":36359,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T06:34:55.000Z"